DATE        AUTHOR      CHANGE
----------- ----------- -------------------------------------------------------
Sep-07-2003 patrickh    Added separate debug and optimized build capabilities.
Aug-31-2003 patrickh    Changed --with-bpldir to --with-boost-python.  The
                        option now specifies the root of the Boost.Python
                        installation tree.
Aug-30-2003 patrickh    Fixed Visual C++ 7.1 (.NET 2003) compile failures.
Aug-20-2003 patrickh    Split PyJuggler back up into multiple Python modules.
                        On Windows, the modules have the extension .pyd.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.8.2
Aug-18-2003 patrickh    Exposed vrj::OsgApp so that developers can combine
                        PyJuggler and PyOSG.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.8.1
Aug-03-2003 patrickh    Updated to JCCL 0.12, Gadgeteer 0.13, and VR Juggler
                        1.1.144.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.8.0
Jul-09-2003 patrickh    Reorganized the way the modules are exposed to Python
                        so that the code can be loaded from a single DSO/DLL.
                        This is being done to fix runtime loader problems on
                        Windows.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.7.1
Jun-30-2003 patrickh    Separated the source for the vpr, gadget, and vrj
                        modules into multiple .cpp files.
Jun-26-2003 patrickh    Removed the vjAvatar bindings.  They now live along
                        side the vjAvatar C++ code.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.7.0
Jun-13-2003 patrickh    Removed setter methods from vrj.Display and related
                        classes.  These now act as read-only objects when
                        accessed from Python.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.6.0
May-21-2003 patrickh    Updated to Gadgeteer 0.12.0 API.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.5.1
May-21-2003 patrickh    Removed the GMTL bindings.  They now live in the PyGMTL
                        project.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.5.0
May-02-2003 patrickh    Exposed vrj::Frustum().
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.13
May-02-2003 patrickh    Exposed gmtl::setFrustum() and gmtl::setPerspective().
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.12
May-02-2003 patrickh    gmtl.intersect() now returns a tuple with varying
                        information depending on the intersection test being
                        performed.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.11
May-01-2003 patrickh    Exposed the getData() method for gmtl::VecBase,
                        gmtl::Quat, and gmtl::EulerAngle.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.10
Apr-30-2003 patrickh    Added vrj::Viewport, vrj::SimViewport, vrj::Display,
                        and vrj::Projection.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.9
Apr-30-2003 patrickh    Updated to Gadgeteer 0.11.1 API.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.8
Apr-30-2003 patrickh    Updated to Gadgeteer 0.11.0 API.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.7
Apr-29-2003 patrickh    Exposed new event window classes in Gadgeteer.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.6
Apr-29-2003 patrickh    Exposed vjAvatar and vjAvatar factory.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.5
Apr-26-2003 patrickh    Exposed common instances of gmtl::Coord<S, T>.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.4
Apr-25-2003 patrickh    Updated to GMTL 0.3.1.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.3
Apr-18-2003 patrickh    Enabled the use of overloaded operators with GMTL
                        objects.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.2
Apr-18-2003 patrickh    Updated to GMTL 0.3.0.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.1
Apr-18-2003 patrickh    Moved C++ utility code into the new pyjutil library
                        directory.  As part of this, PyJuggler::MethodGuard
                        has been renamed to PyJuggler::InterpreterGuard.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.4.0
Apr-16-2003 patrickh    Improved the stability of code based on PyJuggler.vrj
                        by synchronizing multi-threaded access to the Python 
                        interpreter.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.3.1
Apr-11-2003 patrickh    Moved the individual modules into the PyJuggler
                        namespace.  Now we have PyJuggler.vpr, PyJuggler.vrj,
                        and so on.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.3
Apr-11-2003 patrickh    Removed PyJuggler.cpp because the individual modules
                        (gmtl.cpp, vpr.cpp, gadget.cpp, jccl.cpp, vrj.cpp) seem
                        to be as stable sa the old monolithic module.
                        NEW VERSION: 0.2
Apr-11-2003 patrickh    ChangeLog started
